麼時候玩得，官方仍未給出明確的答案。近日，一間丹麥零售商列出 PS5 的價格和發售日，但他訂定的價格明顯超過玩家的預期。<br />\n疑似 PS5 首發價<br />\n<br />\nSony 的首席財務官 Hiroki Totoki 2 月曾指出，當時並未為 PS5 訂定價格，但很多玩家和外國遊戲媒體都認為，PS5 的定價大約落在 450-499 美元之間（約HK$3,489-$3,869）。原因是根據以往 Sony 對 PlayStation 主機的定訂，都幾乎是以接近成本價推出，以擴大玩家人數為目標，在遊戲和配件上獲利，而並不是主機。因此，就算 PS5 在硬件上有強大的升級，玩家也估計 PS5 的價格不會高於 PS4 太多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200331/321642007716040704.jpeg/ZYatwQjRqeR6fZQZ-RoY8fAFv_yU2pMbU7jUSVO41Ek?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200331%2F321642007716040704.jpeg%2FZYatwQjRqeR6fZQZ-RoY8fAFv_yU2pMbU7jUSVO41Ek%3Fv%3Dw960&h=18bd7a1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPS5 價格﹑發售日和遊戲都是玩家關注的內容，但目前仍未有官方消息（Google 圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200331/321658705575809024.png/-11vA82SXfPWRk7X1KjhGty7AFSczGQAgwRqloMEapY?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200331%2F321658705575809024.png%2F-11vA82SXfPWRk7X1KjhGty7AFSczGQAgwRqloMEapY%3Fv%3Dw960&h=65b345d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n丹麥零售商開出 PS4 首發價 3 倍的定價（「f&oslash;tex」網站截圖）<br />\n貴 PS4 近 3 倍的售價？<br />\n<br />\n但丹麥零售商「f&oslash;tex」近日在網站上標出的 PS5 價格，則與玩家的想法背道而馳，竟訂定售價為 6,989 丹麥克朗（約 1,043美元／$8,087），幾乎是 PS4 首發價的 3 倍，更寫到出貨日為 2020 年 12 月 1 日。當然在官方發布前，這個價錢只能當是一個估值，但為什麼「f&oslash;tex」會開出如此誇張的價錢呢？原因或和新冠肺炎有關。Sony 早前已經向玩家大派定心丸，指出 PS5 會如期在 2020 年推出。但因疫情影響，大部分廠房的產品下降，在供應短缺的情況下，PS5 主機的首批主機價格的確有機會偏高，或「f&oslash;tex」的定價可能是炒價。<br />\n<br />\n不知名網都有得訂 PS5<br />\n<br />\n出現 1,043 美元售價 PS5 的同時，一個名為「Play N Trade」的網站就以 395 美元價格開放訂購 PS5。價錢上應該是一個非常吸引和合理的水平，但是「Play N Trade」的網站非常簡陋，可信性成疑。而越接近 PS5 推出的日子，網上 PS5 收訂的情況也應該越多，玩家要小心留意該網站或零售商的信譽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%8B%95%E6%BC%AB/454912/ps5-%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC-%E9%A6%96%E7%99%BC%E6%97%A5%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B-%E4%B8%B9%E9%BA%A5%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%95%86%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E8%B6%85%E8%B2%B4%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC-%E8%BF%91-ps4-%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;utm_campaign=otakuparty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25BC%25AB%2F454912%2Fps5-%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25A0%25BC-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B-%25E4%25B8%25B9%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E9%259B%25B6%25E5%2594%25AE%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%25E8%25B6%2585%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25A0%25BC-%25E8%25BF%2591-ps4-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2580%258D%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost%26utm_campaign%3Dotakuparty&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnTk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=2819b620\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%8B%95%E6%BC%AB/454912/ps5-%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC-%E9%A6%96%E7%99%BC%E6%97%A5%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B-%E4%B8%B9%E9%BA%A5%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%95%86%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E8%B6%85%E8%B2%B4%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC-%E8%BF%91-ps4-%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;utm_campaign=otakuparty</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"PS4 pro銷量大增"},{"pid":"71d7fdd4b9f6c323a8db91a0a1702ad921ce885e","tid":1953573,"uid":174692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"買個位唔智障<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出呢個post 個位先智障"},{"pid":"2aa9af0f93ff6067a34dba7b02385bb1ac0ff839","tid":1953573,"uid":162920,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3ae1c658bfd315e4e6979026e975e3941cc7510c","tid":1953573,"uid":56731,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"quote":{"pid":"837fbbc4c8bab389fd3d39310f1f43ff8bf852d7","tid":1953573,"uid":76216,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"你信呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:01:14.000Z","msg":"今日愚人節，愚蠢既人既節日<br />\n我勸你俾下面好，我唔想搞大佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"唔係今日發生"},{"pid":"50cdff3c83f4900b9a739a4643ec8242c4fc70e3","tid":1953573,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote